<font color="#FF0000">A MESSAGE FOR THE SEASON</font><br>
<tt>Mon Dec 15  1:53:27 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I, as have the others, enjoy the knowledge that you are up and reading.  Don't feel like you have to do anything more than you already have.  This site is much richer from the stories, anecdotes and information you have already posted here.  I have enjoyed the unique pleasure of having corresponded with you.  You are truly one in a million.<br><br>
Your duty now is to your family first, to heal, to enjoy, and to be a Father.  This, after all, is the most important thing we do in life.  All else, all the words, all the duties, all the responsibilities we have had pale in comparison to that of being a Father.  <br><br>
Enjoy the holidays.  This is my message to you and all the others reading this site.  <br><br>
All Our Love,<br><br>
John<br>

<p><code>-- searat@sorcom.com  (John C. Ratliff) </code><p>


